{"word":"H4908 - מִשְׁכָּן - mishkân - mish-kawn' - Dwelleth","slug":"H4908","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מִשְׁכָּן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mishkân"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mish-kawn'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Dwelleth"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05DF; - mishka&#x0302;n</b> - <i>mish-kawn'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H7931\">H7931</a>; a <i>residence</i> (including a shepherd&rsquo;s <i>hut</i>, the <i>lair</i> of animals, figuratively the <i>grave</i>; also the <i>Temple</i>); specifically the <i>Tabernacle</i> (properly its wooden walls): - dwelleth, dwelling (place), habitation, tabernacle, tent."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7931\">H7931</a>, <a href=\"#/H7933\">H7933</a>, <a href=\"#/H7934\">H7934</a>, <a href=\"#/H7935\">H7935</a>"}]}